{
  "video_id": "rQy4gPjUY-s",
  "title": "Why I have coffee with people who send me hate mail | Ã–zlem Cekic",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12960.0,
      "end_time": 17536.0,
      "text": "My inbox is full of hate mails and personal abuse"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17560.0,
      "end_time": 18919.0,
      "text": "and has been for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20240.0,
      "end_time": 24336.0,
      "text": "In 2010, I started answering those mails"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24360.0,
      "end_time": 28759.0,
      "text": "and suggesting to the writer that we might meet for coffee and a chat."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30160.0,
      "end_time": 32280.0,
      "text": "I have had hundreds of encounters."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33640.0,
      "end_time": 37120.0,
      "text": "They have taught me something important that I want to share with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 39560.0,
      "end_time": 42576.0,
      "text": "I was born in Turkey from Kurdish parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 42600.0,
      "end_time": 45280.0,
      "text": "and we moved to Denmark when I was a young child."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 46200.0,
      "end_time": 50136.0,
      "text": "In 2007, I ran for a seat in the Danish parliament"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 50160.0,
      "end_time": 53800.0,
      "text": "as one of the first women with a minority background."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 54400.0,
      "end_time": 55536.0,
      "text": "I was elected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 55560.0,
      "end_time": 59536.0,
      "text": "but I soon found out that not everyone was happy about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 59560.0,
      "end_time": 64760.0,
      "text": "as I had to quickly get used to finding hate messages in my inbox."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 66840.0,
      "end_time": 70936.0,
      "text": "Those emails would begin with something like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 70960.0,
      "end_time": 73800.0,
      "text": "\"What&#39;s a raghead like you doing in our parliament?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 75000.0,
      "end_time": 76616.0,
      "text": "I never answered."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 76640.0,
      "end_time": 78736.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d just delete the emails."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78760.0,
      "end_time": 82920.0,
      "text": "I just thought that the senders and I had nothing in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 83920.0,
      "end_time": 85936.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t understand me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 85960.0,
      "end_time": 88279.0,
      "text": "and I didn&#39;t understand them."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 89880.0,
      "end_time": 92976.0,
      "text": "Then one day, one of my colleagues in the parliament said"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 93000.0,
      "end_time": 95400.0,
      "text": "that I should save the hate mails."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 96800.0,
      "end_time": 99360.0,
      "text": "\"When something happens to you, it will give the police a lead.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 100120.0,
      "end_time": 101856.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 101880.0,
      "end_time": 106136.0,
      "text": "I noticed that she said, \"When something happens\" and not \"if.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 106160.0,
      "end_time": 107800.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 108480.0,
      "end_time": 112520.0,
      "text": "Sometimes hateful letters were also sent to my home address."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 113440.0,
      "end_time": 116976.0,
      "text": "The more I became involved in public debate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 117000.0,
      "end_time": 119600.0,
      "text": "the more hate mail and threats I received."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 121800.0,
      "end_time": 123576.0,
      "text": "After a while, I got a secret address"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 123600.0,
      "end_time": 126919.0,
      "text": "and I had to take extra precautions to protect my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 129840.0,
      "end_time": 133776.0,
      "text": "Then in 2010, a Nazi began to harass me."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 133800.0,
      "end_time": 137280.0,
      "text": "It was a man who had attacked Muslim women on the street."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 138320.0,
      "end_time": 141160.0,
      "text": "Over time, it became much worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 142479.0,
      "end_time": 147200.0,
      "text": "I was at the zoo with my children, and the phone was ringing constantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 148240.0,
      "end_time": 149520.0,
      "text": "It was the Nazi."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 150560.0,
      "end_time": 153536.0,
      "text": "I had the impression that he was close."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 153560.0,
      "end_time": 154760.0,
      "text": "We headed home."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 155800.0,
      "end_time": 157576.0,
      "text": "When we got back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 157600.0,
      "end_time": 163576.0,
      "text": "my son asked, \"Why does he hate you so much, Mom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 163600.0,
      "end_time": 165519.0,
      "text": "when he doesn&#39;t even know you?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 167960.0,
      "end_time": 169920.0,
      "text": "\"Some people are just stupid,\" I said."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 170800.0,
      "end_time": 174320.0,
      "text": "And at the time, I actually thought that was a pretty clever answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 175520.0,
      "end_time": 178760.0,
      "text": "And I suspect that that is the answer most of us would give."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 179560.0,
      "end_time": 180760.0,
      "text": "The others --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 181600.0,
      "end_time": 184519.0,
      "text": "they are stupid, brainwashed, ignorant."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 185640.0,
      "end_time": 189359.0,
      "text": "We are the good guys and they are the bad guys, period."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 191200.0,
      "end_time": 193616.0,
      "text": "Several weeks later I was at a friend&#39;s house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 193640.0,
      "end_time": 199559.0,
      "text": "and I was very upset and angry about all the hate and racism I had met."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 200840.0,
      "end_time": 203856.0,
      "text": "It was he who suggested that I should call them up"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 203880.0,
      "end_time": 205790.0,
      "text": "and visit them."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 206680.0,
      "end_time": 208120.0,
      "text": "\"They will kill me,\" I said."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 209560.0,
      "end_time": 213960.0,
      "text": "\"They would never attack a member of the Danish Parliament,\" he said."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 213120.0,
      "end_time": 217136.0,
      "text": "\"And anyway, if they killed you, you would become a martyr.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 217160.0,
      "end_time": 219296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 219320.0,
      "end_time": 221896.0,
      "text": "\"So it&#39;s pure win-win situation for you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 221920.0,
      "end_time": 224160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 225880.0,
      "end_time": 228656.0,
      "text": "His advice was so unexpected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 228680.0,
      "end_time": 229936.0,
      "text": "when I got home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 229960.0,
      "end_time": 231216.0,
      "text": "I turned on my computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 231240.0,
      "end_time": 234720.0,
      "text": "and opened the folder where I had saved all the hate mail."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 235760.0,
      "end_time": 237600.0,
      "text": "There were literally hundreds of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 238600.0,
      "end_time": 243550.0,
      "text": "Emails that started with words like \"terrorist,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 243800.0,
      "end_time": 244696.0,
      "text": "\"raghead,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 244720.0,
      "end_time": 246200.0,
      "text": "\"rat,\" \"whore.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 248120.0,
      "end_time": 251600.0,
      "text": "I decided to contact the one who had sent me the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 252920.0,
      "end_time": 254679.0,
      "text": "His name was Ingolf."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 257790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262840.0,
      "text": "I decided to contact him just once so I could say at least I had tried."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 263880.0,
      "end_time": 266576.0,
      "text": "To my surprise and shock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 266600.0,
      "end_time": 267920.0,
      "text": "he answered the phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 268959.0,
      "end_time": 273896.0,
      "text": "I blurted out, \"Hello, my name is Ã–zlem. You have sent me so many hate mails."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 273920.0,
      "end_time": 275656.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t know me, I don&#39;t know you."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 275680.0,
      "end_time": 279136.0,
      "text": "I was wondering if I could come around and we can drink a coffee together"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 279160.0,
      "end_time": 280416.0,
      "text": "and talk about it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 280440.0,
      "end_time": 282760.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 283920.0,
      "end_time": 286200.0,
      "text": "There was silence on the line."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 287160.0,
      "end_time": 288760.0,
      "text": "And then he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 290160.0,
      "end_time": 292960.0,
      "text": "\"I have to ask my wife.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 292120.0,
      "end_time": 293496.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 293520.0,
      "end_time": 294736.0,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 294760.0,
      "end_time": 296176.0,
      "text": "The racist has a wife?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 296200.0,
      "end_time": 298560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 298800.0,
      "end_time": 301135.0,
      "text": "A couple of days later, we met at his house."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 301160.0,
      "end_time": 305416.0,
      "text": "I will never forget when he opened his front door"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 305440.0,
      "end_time": 307880.0,
      "text": "and reached out to shake my hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 308880.0,
      "end_time": 310896.0,
      "text": "I felt so disappointed."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 310920.0,
      "end_time": 312136.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 312160.0,
      "end_time": 315240.0,
      "text": "because he looked nothing like I&#39;d imagined."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 316400.0,
      "end_time": 319296.0,
      "text": "I had expected a horrible person --"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 319320.0,
      "end_time": 321456.0,
      "text": "dirty, messy house."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 321480.0,
      "end_time": 322720.0,
      "text": "It was not."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 323720.0,
      "end_time": 325496.0,
      "text": "His house smelled of coffee"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 325520.0,
      "end_time": 329520.0,
      "text": "which was served from a coffee set identical to the one my parents used."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 330760.0,
      "end_time": 333320.0,
      "text": "I ended up staying for two and a half hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 334840.0,
      "end_time": 337960.0,
      "text": "And we had so many things in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 339120.0,
      "end_time": 341936.0,
      "text": "Even our prejudices were alike."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 341960.0,
      "end_time": 343856.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 343880.0,
      "end_time": 346936.0,
      "text": "Ingolf told me that when he waits for the bus"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 346960.0,
      "end_time": 350416.0,
      "text": "and the bus stops 10 meters away from him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 350440.0,
      "end_time": 353400.0,
      "text": "it was because the driver was a \"raghead.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 355120.0,
      "end_time": 357160.0,
      "text": "I recognized that feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 357400.0,
      "end_time": 358320.0,
      "text": "When I was young"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 359560.0,
      "end_time": 361560.0,
      "text": "and I waited for the bus"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 361800.0,
      "end_time": 363135.0,
      "text": "and it stopped 10 meters away from me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 363160.0,
      "end_time": 365600.0,
      "text": "I was sure that the driver was a racist."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 369600.0,
      "end_time": 371696.0,
      "text": "When I got home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 371720.0,
      "end_time": 374160.0,
      "text": "I was very ambivalent about my experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 375120.0,
      "end_time": 377720.0,
      "text": "On the one hand, I really liked Ingolf."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 378920.0,
      "end_time": 382160.0,
      "text": "He was easy and pleasant to talk to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 383400.0,
      "end_time": 384976.0,
      "text": "but on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 385000.0,
      "end_time": 389696.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t stand the idea of having so much in common"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 389720.0,
      "end_time": 392920.0,
      "text": "with someone who had such clearly racist views."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 396800.0,
      "end_time": 397296.0,
      "text": "Gradually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 397320.0,
      "end_time": 399160.0,
      "text": "and painfully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 399400.0,
      "end_time": 400296.0,
      "text": "I came to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 400320.0,
      "end_time": 405200.0,
      "text": "that I had been just as judgmental of those who had sent me hate mails"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 406320.0,
      "end_time": 408800.0,
      "text": "as they had been of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 410640.0,
      "end_time": 415599.0,
      "text": "This was the beginning of what I call #dialoguecoffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 416960.0,
      "end_time": 419560.0,
      "text": "Basically, I sit down for coffee"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 419800.0,
      "end_time": 422895.0,
      "text": "with people who have said the most terrible things to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 422920.0,
      "end_time": 426736.0,
      "text": "to try to understand why they hate people like me"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 426760.0,
      "end_time": 428599.0,
      "text": "when they don&#39;t even know me."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 430800.0,
      "end_time": 433160.0,
      "text": "I have been doing this the last eight years."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 434760.0,
      "end_time": 438176.0,
      "text": "The vast majority of people I approach agree to meet me."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 438200.0,
      "end_time": 439536.0,
      "text": "Most of them are men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 439560.0,
      "end_time": 441400.0,
      "text": "but I have also met women."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 442000.0,
      "end_time": 445896.0,
      "text": "I have made it a rule to always meet them in their house"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 445920.0,
      "end_time": 448320.0,
      "text": "to convey from the outset that I trust them."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 448960.0,
      "end_time": 452775.0,
      "text": "I always bring food because when we eat together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 452800.0,
      "end_time": 455216.0,
      "text": "it is easier to find what we have in common"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 455240.0,
      "end_time": 456720.0,
      "text": "and make peace together."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 458480.0,
      "end_time": 462896.0,
      "text": "Along the way, I have learned some valuable lessons."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 462920.0,
      "end_time": 466160.0,
      "text": "The people who sent hate mails are workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 466400.0,
      "end_time": 468336.0,
      "text": "husbands, wives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 468360.0,
      "end_time": 469720.0,
      "text": "parents like you and me."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 470520.0,
      "end_time": 474856.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not saying that their behavior is acceptable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 474880.0,
      "end_time": 479616.0,
      "text": "but I have learned to distance myself from the hateful views"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 479640.0,
      "end_time": 485240.0,
      "text": "without distancing myself from the person who&#39;s expressing those views."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 487240.0,
      "end_time": 489296.0,
      "text": "And I have discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 489320.0,
      "end_time": 494216.0,
      "text": "that the people I visit are just as afraid of people they don&#39;t know"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 494240.0,
      "end_time": 499320.0,
      "text": "as I was afraid of them before I started inviting myself for coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 501440.0,
      "end_time": 504936.0,
      "text": "During these meetings, a specific theme keeps coming up."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 504960.0,
      "end_time": 509296.0,
      "text": "It shows up regardless whether I&#39;m talking to a humanist or a racist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 509320.0,
      "end_time": 510816.0,
      "text": "a man, a woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 510840.0,
      "end_time": 512895.0,
      "text": "a Muslim or an atheist."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 512919.0,
      "end_time": 514856.0,
      "text": "They all seem to think"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 514880.0,
      "end_time": 518150.0,
      "text": "that other people are to blame for the hate"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 518390.0,
      "end_time": 520295.0,
      "text": "and for the generalization of groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 520320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525560.0,
      "text": "They all believe that other people have to stop demonizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 525800.0,
      "end_time": 527856.0,
      "text": "They point at politicians, the media, their neighbor"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 527880.0,
      "end_time": 530320.0,
      "text": "or the bus driver who stops 10 meters away."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 531600.0,
      "end_time": 534200.0,
      "text": "But when I asked, \"What about you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 535390.0,
      "end_time": 536280.0,
      "text": "What can you do?\","
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 537360.0,
      "end_time": 539576.0,
      "text": "the reply is usually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 539600.0,
      "end_time": 541376.0,
      "text": "\"What can I do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 541400.0,
      "end_time": 543456.0,
      "text": "I have no influence."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 543480.0,
      "end_time": 545160.0,
      "text": "I have no power.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 546400.0,
      "end_time": 548336.0,
      "text": "I know that feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 548360.0,
      "end_time": 549976.0,
      "text": "For a large part of my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 550000.0,
      "end_time": 555976.0,
      "text": "I also thought that I didn&#39;t have any power or influence --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 556000.0,
      "end_time": 558920.0,
      "text": "even when I was a member of the Danish parliament."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 560120.0,
      "end_time": 562856.0,
      "text": "But today I know the reality is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 562880.0,
      "end_time": 565776.0,
      "text": "We all have power and influence where we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 565800.0,
      "end_time": 568216.0,
      "text": "so we must never,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 568240.0,
      "end_time": 571520.0,
      "text": "never underestimate our own potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 575400.0,
      "end_time": 577960.0,
      "text": "The #dialoguecoffee meetings have taught me"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 577120.0,
      "end_time": 581136.0,
      "text": "that people of all political convictions can be caught demonizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 581160.0,
      "end_time": 583000.0,
      "text": "the others with different views."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 584000.0,
      "end_time": 585856.0,
      "text": "I know what I&#39;m talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 585880.0,
      "end_time": 590576.0,
      "text": "As a young child, I hated different population groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 590600.0,
      "end_time": 593760.0,
      "text": "And at the time, my religious views were very extreme."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 594720.0,
      "end_time": 599456.0,
      "text": "But my friendship with Turks, with Danes, with Jews and with racists"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 599480.0,
      "end_time": 602840.0,
      "text": "has vaccinated me against my own prejudices."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 604280.0,
      "end_time": 606456.0,
      "text": "I grew up in a working-class family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 606480.0,
      "end_time": 612800.0,
      "text": "and on my journey I have met many people who have insisted on speaking to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 613120.0,
      "end_time": 614680.0,
      "text": "They have changed my views."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 616160.0,
      "end_time": 620280.0,
      "text": "They have formed me as a democratic citizen and a bridge builder."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 622000.0,
      "end_time": 624296.0,
      "text": "If you want to prevent hate and violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 624320.0,
      "end_time": 627736.0,
      "text": "we have to talk to as many people as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 627760.0,
      "end_time": 630560.0,
      "text": "for as long as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 630800.0,
      "end_time": 632280.0,
      "text": "while being as open as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 633120.0,
      "end_time": 636376.0,
      "text": "That can only be achieved through debate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 636400.0,
      "end_time": 638295.0,
      "text": "critical conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 638320.0,
      "end_time": 642320.0,
      "text": "and insisting on dialogue that doesn&#39;t demonize people."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 644960.0,
      "end_time": 646640.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to ask you a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 647520.0,
      "end_time": 651816.0,
      "text": "I invite you to think about it when you get home and in the coming days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 651840.0,
      "end_time": 654536.0,
      "text": "but you have to be honest with yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 654560.0,
      "end_time": 656959.0,
      "text": "It should be easy, no one else will know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 658560.0,
      "end_time": 660000.0,
      "text": "The question is this ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 662600.0,
      "end_time": 664120.0,
      "text": "who do you demonize?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 666600.0,
      "end_time": 670800.0,
      "text": "Do you think supporters of American President Trump are deplorables?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 672920.0,
      "end_time": 678360.0,
      "text": "Or that those who voted for Turkish President ErdoÄŸan are crazy Islamists?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 680360.0,
      "end_time": 685440.0,
      "text": "Or that those who voted for Le Pen in France are stupid fascists?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 687480.0,
      "end_time": 691576.0,
      "text": "Or perhaps you think that Americans who voted for Bernie Sanders"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 691600.0,
      "end_time": 693216.0,
      "text": "are immature hippies."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 693240.0,
      "end_time": 694760.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 695800.0,
      "end_time": 699839.0,
      "text": "All those words have been used to vilify those groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 701640.0,
      "end_time": 705560.0,
      "text": "Maybe at this point, do you think I am an idealist?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 708280.0,
      "end_time": 710776.0,
      "text": "I want to give you a challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 710800.0,
      "end_time": 712575.0,
      "text": "Before the end of this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 712600.0,
      "end_time": 717296.0,
      "text": "I challenge you to invite someone who you demonize --"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 717320.0,
      "end_time": 721376.0,
      "text": "someone who you disagree with politically and/or culturally"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 721400.0,
      "end_time": 723720.0,
      "text": "and don&#39;t think you have anything in common with."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 726440.0,
      "end_time": 729760.0,
      "text": "I challenge you to invite someone like this to #dialoguecoffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 731360.0,
      "end_time": 732560.0,
      "text": "Remember Ingolf?"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 733320.0,
      "end_time": 737416.0,
      "text": "Basically, I&#39;m asking you to find an Ingolf in your life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 737440.0,
      "end_time": 739960.0,
      "text": "contact him or her"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 739120.0,
      "end_time": 741600.0,
      "text": "and suggest that you can meet for #dialoguecofee."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 743200.0,
      "end_time": 746656.0,
      "text": "When you start at #dialoguecoffee, you have to remember this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 746680.0,
      "end_time": 751776.0,
      "text": "first, don&#39;t give up if the person refuses at first."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 751800.0,
      "end_time": 755800.0,
      "text": "Sometimes it&#39;s taken me nearly one year to arrange a #dialoguecoffee meeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 756600.0,
      "end_time": 757856.0,
      "text": "Two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 757880.0,
      "end_time": 760256.0,
      "text": "acknowledge the other person&#39;s courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 760280.0,
      "end_time": 762576.0,
      "text": "It isn&#39;t just you who&#39;s brave."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 762600.0,
      "end_time": 766736.0,
      "text": "The one who&#39;s inviting you into their home is just as brave."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 766760.0,
      "end_time": 768960.0,
      "text": "Three:"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 768120.0,
      "end_time": 770416.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t judge during the conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 770440.0,
      "end_time": 774280.0,
      "text": "Make sure that most of the conversation focuses on what you have in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 775640.0,
      "end_time": 777240.0,
      "text": "As I said, bring food."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 778120.0,
      "end_time": 782416.0,
      "text": "And finally, remember to finish the conversation in a positive way"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 782440.0,
      "end_time": 784456.0,
      "text": "because you are going to meet again."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 784480.0,
      "end_time": 787280.0,
      "text": "A bridge can&#39;t be built in one day."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 789640.0,
      "end_time": 794456.0,
      "text": "We are living in a world where many people hold definitive and often extreme opinions"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 794480.0,
      "end_time": 795696.0,
      "text": "about the others"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 795720.0,
      "end_time": 797320.0,
      "text": "without knowing much about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 798000.0,
      "end_time": 804176.0,
      "text": "We notice of course the prejudices on the other side than in our own bases."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 804200.0,
      "end_time": 806200.0,
      "text": "And we ban them from our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 807440.0,
      "end_time": 808760.0,
      "text": "We delete the hate mails."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 809600.0,
      "end_time": 812776.0,
      "text": "We hang out only with people who think like us"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 812800.0,
      "end_time": 815520.0,
      "text": "and talk about the others in a category of disdain."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 816960.0,
      "end_time": 819176.0,
      "text": "We unfriend people on Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 819200.0,
      "end_time": 822376.0,
      "text": "and when we meet people who are discriminating"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 822400.0,
      "end_time": 824136.0,
      "text": "or dehumanizing people or groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 824160.0,
      "end_time": 828640.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t insist on speaking with them to challenge their opinions."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 830720.0,
      "end_time": 835176.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how healthy democratic societies break down --"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 835200.0,
      "end_time": 838520.0,
      "text": "when we don&#39;t check the personal responsibility for the democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 840240.0,
      "end_time": 842160.0,
      "text": "We take the democracy for granted."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 843200.0,
      "end_time": 844400.0,
      "text": "It is not."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 846120.0,
      "end_time": 849880.0,
      "text": "Conversation is the most difficult thing in a democracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 850920.0,
      "end_time": 854000.0,
      "text": "and also the most important."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 856800.0,
      "end_time": 857520.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s my challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 858760.0,
      "end_time": 860415.0,
      "text": "Find your Ingolf."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 860440.0,
      "end_time": 861456.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 861480.0,
      "end_time": 863160.0,
      "text": "Start a conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 863760.0,
      "end_time": 867295.0,
      "text": "Trenches have been dug between people, yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 867320.0,
      "end_time": 872720.0,
      "text": "but we all have the ability to build the bridges that cross the trenches."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 875560.0,
      "end_time": 878496.0,
      "text": "And let me end by quoting my friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 878520.0,
      "end_time": 879720.0,
      "text": "Sergeot Uzan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 880640.0,
      "end_time": 884656.0,
      "text": "who lost his son, Dan Uzan, in a terror attack"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 884680.0,
      "end_time": 887880.0,
      "text": "on a Jewish synagogue in Copenhagen, 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 889480.0,
      "end_time": 892640.0,
      "text": "Sergio rejected any suggestion of revenge"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 893920.0,
      "end_time": 895520.0,
      "text": "and instead said this ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 898160.0,
      "end_time": 902360.0,
      "text": "\"Evil can only be defeated by kindness between people."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 903640.0,
      "end_time": 906720.0,
      "text": "Kindness demands courage.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 907960.0,
      "end_time": 909776.0,
      "text": "Dear friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 909800.0,
      "end_time": 911616.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s be courageous."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 911640.0,
      "end_time": 912856.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 912880.0,
      "end_time": 917439.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}